            </div>

            <p>See also <a href="/generative-engine-optimisation/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">generative engine optimisation</a> for the strategic context these monitoring platforms serve.</p>
