        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-ink-300 leading-relaxed"><strong>Different categories of AI visibility platform produce different management-layer signals.</strong> The table below maps each category to its primary output, the headline metric it surfaces, and the stakeholder use case it best serves — helping marketing leaders identify which platform type fits their reporting and decision-making needs.</p>

